record.text:
You're not nobody, you're anyone.

The PowerShell Community should accept anyone and everyone.

The painful irony here is that I've heard Doug rant a lot about cancel culture over the years.

It's very sad and hypocritical that he is so quick to cancel.

Alt: Abed knows the difference between the real world and tv.

On TV we have heroes, we have good people.

In the real world, we have MVPs who shun anyone who questions them.  We have people who should be helping but instead hurt.

We have Doug.
